"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-sport-sport-olympics-paris-olympics-2024-jack-laugher-onlyfans-b1173071.html\", \"text\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies. Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search. See our privacy policy for more information.  Sport|Olympics  Jack Laugherand some of hisTeam GBdiving teammates have set upOnlyFansaccounts to help fund theirParis Olympics ambitions.  Laugher and other divers deemed with podium potential for theParis Olympicsget funding of \\u00a328,000 a year.  But the 29-year-old admitted he had turned to OnlyFans to supplement his income. Subscription to his page costs $10 (\\u00a37.77) per month with an annual subscription at a reduced rate of \\u00a380.  Laugher, who insists there are no nude pictures, also said other members of the team had also followed suit, including Noah Williams, who willpartner Tom Daleyin the 10metre platform synchro diving competition.  He said: \\\"I try and make extra money. I have got something people want and I will happily cash in on that. I am a bit of a hustler and I want a bit more money if I can.  \\\"I was the first person to do it in our team. Dad was saying to me, 'you put stuff on Instagram for free but when the product is free, like Instagram is, you are the product.  \\\"So now I am giving people stuff which is very similar to what I post online but it's for a small subscription fee.\\\"  MORE ABOUT  Have your say...  1  Crime  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping  2  Football  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and confirmed team news  3  UK  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning over Donald Trump's Iran war  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning on Iran war  4  Lifestyle  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  5  Football  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news, predicted lineup, injury latest for Carabao Cup final  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news and predicted lineup\"}"